snippet.textDisplay: I don't wish for anything. But can God just return my dad please. I can't live. Bahut koshish kar li. Nhi ho rha merese. Bas unko wapas bhej dijiye. Meri family saath rahe ya phir hum teeno ko maut dijiye taki ek sath ho jaye. Duniya mein unke bina kuch bacha nhi h hum teeno k liye. Nhi jee payenge. Wo akele h. Pta nhi kaise honge. Koi nhi h unke pass. Please bhagwaan unko nhi bacha sake toh hum teeno ko hi maut de dijiye.
